\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs all changes to production systems,
 infrastructure,
 configurations,
 and software within the Elko County Information Operations Department (ECIO),
 including the classification,
 authorization,
 documentation,
 and closure requirements for Standard,
 Significant,
 and Emergency changes.
\end_layout

